Title: J'entends plus la guitare
Writer: Marc Cholodenko (dialogue), Philippe Garrel (screenplay), Jean-François Goyet (adaptation)
Actors: Benoît Régent, Johanna ter Steege, Yann Collette, Mireille Perrier
Plot: For those who were young, living under the delusions of love and soft drugs in Paris, May 1968 - even if the guitar is still playing, they can't hear it any longer.
